# ─── Disco Boat Rentals · production redirects ────────────────────────────────
# Site lives at discoboatrentals.com (apex). www is canonicalized to apex.
# Netlify handles HTTPS + apex/www automatically when both are added as custom
# domains, but these explicit rules are a safety belt.

# www → apex (force apex as canonical)
https://www.discoboatrentals.com/*    https://discoboatrentals.com/:splat   301!

# ─── WordPress URL preservation (don't lose existing rankings) ────────────────
# Pages we kept at the same slug — handled by file structure, no redirect needed:
#   /articles/                          → already present
#   /boat-rental-mission-bay/           → already present
#   /disco-party-planning-guide/        → already present

# 301s from old WP URLs that we did NOT carry over
/4135-2                /   301
/4135-2/               /   301

# Common WP URL patterns that won't exist on the new site — send to home
/wp-admin              /   301
/wp-admin/             /   301
/wp-login.php          /   301
/?p=*                  /   301
